WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.416 --> 00:00:13.875
Patriarch. Pioneer.

2
00:00:15.208 --> 00:00:16.375
Icon.

3
00:00:17.875 --> 00:00:20.625
That's what they used to call me.

4
00:00:20.708 --> 00:00:22.000
but now I'm...

5
00:00:22.083 --> 00:00:25.333
It's just journalists
trying to sell papers.

6
00:00:25.416 --> 00:00:27.583
I'm a laughing stock with a weak heart.

7
00:00:28.875 --> 00:00:34.041
And a wife
who slept with his daughter.

8
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:38.500
I've lost my touch.

9
00:00:41.625 --> 00:00:44.958
Things are going to get worse
when this thing with Grace goes public.

10
00:00:46.375 --> 00:00:47.583
I can't believe she...

11
00:00:48.083 --> 00:00:50.625
I'm sorry you had to find out like that.

12
00:00:51.625 --> 00:00:54.583
But. like. I thought you needed to know.

13
00:00:55.958 --> 00:00:58.166
I can't have any more of these failures.

14
00:00:58.958 --> 00:01:00.583
I need to do something...

15
00:01:01.708 --> 00:01:02.916
something big.

16
00:01:04.083 --> 00:01:05.375
Like what?

17
00:01:08.166 --> 00:01:10.166
We're getting married
at the end of this week.

18
00:01:11.041 --> 00:01:13.708
- Bab' Don...
- It's going to be a wedding of the decade.

19
00:01:13.791 --> 00:01:16.291
A reminder that Don Bhengu still got it.

20
00:01:18.875 --> 00:01:20.333
Imagine the headline...

21
00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:25.291
"Don Bhengu weds the Face

22
00:01:26.125 --> 00:01:27.500
of Bhengu!"

23
00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:35.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

24
00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:44.100
How could you do that to Thando?

25
00:01:44.125 --> 00:01:45.125
Really. Phila?

26
00:01:45.208 --> 00:01:47.666
Your father kicked us out
and you want to talk about Thando.

27
00:01:47.750 --> 00:01:49.851
- You aborted her child.
- Don't be crude!

28
00:01:49.875 --> 00:01:52.166
Your father and I were a team.

29
00:01:52.250 --> 00:01:54.125
And then he decided he wants more.

30
00:01:54.208 --> 00:01:56.375
More children. more wives. more bastard...

31
00:01:56.458 --> 00:01:57.809
That doesn't justify what you did.

32
00:01:57.833 --> 00:02:00.083
- I wanted him to suffer. Phila.
- And what about her?

33
00:02:00.166 --> 00:02:03.791
- What about Thando?
- She needed to know her place. Okay?

34
00:02:07.166 --> 00:02:10.458
Ma. I need you to talk to her.

35
00:02:12.041 --> 00:02:13.500
Apologize.

36
00:02:13.583 --> 00:02:17.000
The only thing I need to figure out
is how to deal with your father.

37
00:02:17.083 --> 00:02:18.458
I am serious. Ma.

38
00:02:19.208 --> 00:02:21.708
It's either you apologize
or you're on your own.

39
00:02:35.250 --> 00:02:36.375
Hi. babe.

40
00:02:36.458 --> 00:02:37.458
Hi.

41
00:02:43.583 --> 00:02:44.625
Thando?

42
00:02:45.625 --> 00:02:47.083
Hey. what's wrong?

43
00:02:48.875 --> 00:02:50.000
Are you all right?

44
00:02:53.916 --> 00:02:55.833
I know you're not going
to like this. but...

45
00:02:55.916 --> 00:02:56.833
What?

46
00:02:56.916 --> 00:02:58.083
I saw Zinhle.

47
00:02:59.083 --> 00:03:00.625
- Thando.
- Yes. I know. I know.

48
00:03:00.708 --> 00:03:02.291
But you have to hear this.

49
00:03:02.916 --> 00:03:03.916
Okay...

50
00:03:06.958 --> 00:03:08.333
Don asked Zinhle to marry him.

51
00:03:08.416 --> 00:03:09.750
- What?
- She said yes.

52
00:03:09.833 --> 00:03:12.583
No. no. why would
my Dad marry Zinhle? That...

53
00:03:12.666 --> 00:03:13.791
I don't know.

54
00:03:13.875 --> 00:03:16.125
That's insane. I ca... I can't allow that.

55
00:03:16.208 --> 00:03:17.892
- Who are you calling?
- My father.

56
00:03:17.916 --> 00:03:19.750
I can't allow it to happen.

57
00:03:21.208 --> 00:03:24.458
Yeah. I'm still blocked. Listen.
why... why would he marry Zinhle?

58
00:03:24.541 --> 00:03:25.375
I don't know.

59
00:03:25.458 --> 00:03:26.708
I have no idea.

60
00:03:28.916 --> 00:03:31.375
I found the girl
who filmed us at Emerald.

61
00:03:31.458 --> 00:03:33.625
She gave me a name
and number of who hired her.

62
00:03:33.708 --> 00:03:35.041
I just need to find him.

63
00:03:35.125 --> 00:03:37.708
So. you still think that Zinhle
is behind everything?

64
00:03:38.375 --> 00:03:42.583
Yeah. I... I just need to piece
everything together right now.

65
00:03:45.458 --> 00:03:46.708
Marry her?

66
00:03:46.791 --> 00:03:48.916
I knew that girl was up to something.

67
00:04:13.458 --> 00:04:15.083
Good morning. Bab' Don.

68
00:04:16.583 --> 00:04:18.166
You're about to be my wife.

69
00:04:18.875 --> 00:04:20.000
Please call me Ngcolosi.

70
00:04:21.416 --> 00:04:22.500
Ngcolosi.

71
00:04:29.708 --> 00:04:30.875
I was thinking...

72
00:04:32.791 --> 00:04:36.125
"The wedding of the decade" needs
at least three months of preparation.

73
00:04:37.916 --> 00:04:41.375
That way you get maximum publicity and

74
00:04:41.458 --> 00:04:43.625
you and I can
get to know each other better.

75
00:04:44.291 --> 00:04:47.000
We can always get to know
each other after our wedding.

76
00:04:49.083 --> 00:04:51.750
I'm not about to give Grace
time to spin the story.

77
00:04:52.666 --> 00:04:54.125
One thing I'm not doing...

78
00:04:54.666 --> 00:04:58.375
...is waiting three
months before sleeping with you.

79
00:04:59.375 --> 00:05:00.500
Thomas?

80
00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:03.666
Take those bags to the main bedroom.

81
00:05:07.625 --> 00:05:09.225
I've got something for you.

82
00:05:18.166 --> 00:05:19.375
Give me your hand.

83
00:05:31.333 --> 00:05:32.333
Stunning!

84
00:05:33.708 --> 00:05:36.083
Please do show it off at the shoot.

85
00:05:38.125 --> 00:05:40.375
I don't have a shoot today.

86
00:05:40.875 --> 00:05:43.625
Our wedding announcement shoot.

87
00:05:54.083 --> 00:05:56.708
Look. I don't mean to be rude.
but what do you guys want?

88
00:05:58.166 --> 00:05:59.166
Ma.

89
00:05:59.708 --> 00:06:02.625
If it's about Zinhle and Dad.
we already know. so save it.

90
00:06:02.708 --> 00:06:04.291
No. it's not that.

91
00:06:04.958 --> 00:06:05.958
Okay.

92
00:06:06.666 --> 00:06:07.666
Ma. say something.

93
00:06:12.458 --> 00:06:15.291
I came to apologize for what I did to you.

94
00:06:19.583 --> 00:06:21.583
Well. you've done a lot of things to me.

95
00:06:21.666 --> 00:06:23.416
What exactly are you apologizing for?

96
00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:26.916
Specifically for the loss of your child.

97
00:06:31.833 --> 00:06:34.833
What? Babe. what is she on about? Why...

98
00:06:36.375 --> 00:06:37.416
Baby?

99
00:06:38.291 --> 00:06:40.375
Why are you apologizing for that. Grace?

100
00:06:40.458 --> 00:06:42.375
Because it wasn't a miscarriage.

101
00:06:43.166 --> 00:06:44.791
She put a pill in my drink.

102
00:06:44.875 --> 00:06:47.708
Thando. I'm so sorry.
I was angry with Don. and I took...

103
00:06:47.791 --> 00:06:49.375
Whoa!

104
00:06:49.458 --> 00:06:50.578
Did you know. Phila?

105
00:06:50.625 --> 00:06:52.916
No. I found out last night
when we were kicked out.

106
00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:53.833
What?

107
00:06:53.916 --> 00:06:55.791
Yes. we've all been kicked out.

108
00:06:55.875 --> 00:06:59.416
Look. Zinhle recorded your conversation
and she played it back for Baba.

109
00:07:00.208 --> 00:07:02.583
I just wanted Ma
to come and apologize to you.

110
00:07:02.666 --> 00:07:04.375
You call that an apology?

111
00:07:09.375 --> 00:07:12.000
I think it's best you both leave.

112
00:07:13.416 --> 00:07:14.291
Now.

113
00:07:22.791 --> 00:07:24.750
I'm sorry that we bothered you.

114
00:07:49.166 --> 00:07:50.875
Why didn't you tell me?

115
00:07:52.916 --> 00:07:56.083
Grace would've
made my life hell if I told anyone.

116
00:07:56.166 --> 00:07:57.583
I would've protected you.

117
00:07:58.833 --> 00:08:00.793
I'd have protected you
and you know it.

118
00:08:00.875 --> 00:08:01.875
I know.

119
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.583
And if I told my father.

120
00:08:04.666 --> 00:08:06.708
he definitely would've
kicked her out sooner.

121
00:08:07.708 --> 00:08:10.428
Well. then I would've
been forced to have kids with him.

122
00:08:12.375 --> 00:08:14.041
You know. baby...

123
00:08:16.291 --> 00:08:21.000
You know. you... you're the best thing
that has ever happened to me.

124
00:08:23.750 --> 00:08:25.625
And if I'd had to have kids with him...

125
00:08:27.875 --> 00:08:29.416
this was not going to happen.

126
00:08:38.708 --> 00:08:40.958
Um. sorry. it's Zandi.

127
00:08:41.708 --> 00:08:43.125
Yeah. it's okay.

128
00:08:47.041 --> 00:08:48.125
She says...

129
00:08:48.208 --> 00:08:51.000
she's going to help us
find out who this Bonga person is.

130
00:08:57.208 --> 00:08:58.583
Will you be okay here alone?

131
00:08:59.916 --> 00:09:00.833
You sure?

132
00:09:00.916 --> 00:09:02.333
Yeah. go.

133
00:09:28.875 --> 00:09:32.750
<i>♪ All my love scattered everywhere ♪</i>

134
00:09:34.125 --> 00:09:35.875
<i>♪ What do you care? ♪</i>

135
00:09:37.416 --> 00:09:41.958
<i>♪ What seemed so sweet
Turned into a nightmare ♪</i>

136
00:09:42.750 --> 00:09:44.750
<i>♪ I was so scared ♪</i>

137
00:09:46.041 --> 00:09:49.916
<i>♪ The beating stops and I panic ♪</i>

138
00:09:50.500 --> 00:09:54.000
<i>♪ Then I become so mechanic... ♪</i>

139
00:09:56.958 --> 00:09:59.583
Things are getting
out of hand. It's a mess.

140
00:10:00.833 --> 00:10:03.875
You know. I didn't think
he'd get rid of Grace.

141
00:10:03.958 --> 00:10:05.878
But when he did. I thought. "Great."

142
00:10:05.916 --> 00:10:09.583
<i>I thought it would
be easier to get a confession from him.</i>

143
00:10:10.333 --> 00:10:11.375
Okay.

144
00:10:11.458 --> 00:10:13.166
<i>What's going on? Talk.</i>

145
00:10:13.250 --> 00:10:15.958
He wants to marry me.
By the end of this week.

146
00:10:16.041 --> 00:10:17.625
<i>Are you listening to yourself?</i>

147
00:10:18.166 --> 00:10:22.458
So. you marry him at the end
of the week and then what? Hmm?

148
00:10:22.541 --> 00:10:23.833
You know how Don is.

149
00:10:23.916 --> 00:10:26.333
And knowing him. he's going to want more.

150
00:10:28.166 --> 00:10:30.958
Sister... what are you going to do?

151
00:10:33.416 --> 00:10:37.625
<i>Do you remember the day we had
Amahle's cleansing. you told me that</i>

152
00:10:39.125 --> 00:10:42.291
you want Don to suffer. Remember?

153
00:10:42.375 --> 00:10:43.250
I know.

154
00:10:43.333 --> 00:10:45.083
<i>But he's not the one
who is suffering now.</i>

155
00:10:45.166 --> 00:10:46.541
We are suffering!

156
00:10:49.666 --> 00:10:50.666
My sister...

157
00:10:50.708 --> 00:10:53.908
- we're losing ourselves here.
- Bonga. I'll make a plan.

158
00:10:54.625 --> 00:10:55.666
<i>Okay. okay.</i>

159
00:10:55.750 --> 00:10:56.833
<i>Listen.</i>

160
00:10:58.083 --> 00:10:59.708
<i>There's something you need to know.</i>

161
00:10:59.791 --> 00:11:00.958
Cleansing.

162
00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.833
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

163
00:11:05.791 --> 00:11:06.791
Thanks. brother.

164
00:11:07.333 --> 00:11:10.791
I think I know how
we'll get a confession from Don.

165
00:11:11.291 --> 00:11:12.333
<i>Zinhle?</i>

166
00:11:12.416 --> 00:11:13.708
I'll call you.

167
00:11:14.666 --> 00:11:15.541
Zee?

168
00:11:18.833 --> 00:11:19.833
Yeah.

169
00:11:20.416 --> 00:11:22.375
Just draw something
up for me in the meantime

170
00:11:22.458 --> 00:11:24.166
and then we'll finalize later. yeah?

171
00:11:24.250 --> 00:11:25.250
Cool.

172
00:11:28.958 --> 00:11:30.791
Okay. one down.

173
00:11:30.875 --> 00:11:32.291
What you working on?

174
00:11:32.375 --> 00:11:36.250
I am looking for the best
divorce lawyers in the country.

175
00:11:37.125 --> 00:11:38.625
For whose divorce?

176
00:11:39.625 --> 00:11:42.375
Yours. Isn't that
what you're going to do. start over?

177
00:11:42.458 --> 00:11:45.541
Son. I really don't have
the energy to start over.

178
00:11:47.875 --> 00:11:50.708
Okay. Then what are you going to do?

179
00:11:51.500 --> 00:11:53.125
There's something I never told you...

180
00:11:53.208 --> 00:11:55.048
...about how
we started the company.

181
00:11:56.250 --> 00:11:59.250
Your father and I
were going to co-own it fifty-fifty.

182
00:11:59.333 --> 00:12:01.083
But he went behind my back...

183
00:12:01.166 --> 00:12:03.583
...and registered everything in his name.

184
00:12:03.666 --> 00:12:06.375
I convinced myself
that what's his was also mine.

185
00:12:07.291 --> 00:12:10.333
But he never let me forget who was boss.

186
00:12:10.416 --> 00:12:11.708
This time he has gone too far.

187
00:12:11.791 --> 00:12:13.083
He'll never change.

188
00:12:13.166 --> 00:12:15.625
Okay. Well. isn't that
why you should divorce him?

189
00:12:15.708 --> 00:12:18.416
So you can get back your dignity
and half of what's yours?

190
00:12:20.041 --> 00:12:21.500
Did you say "half"?

191
00:12:22.208 --> 00:12:24.583
No. my child. I don't do half.

192
00:12:24.666 --> 00:12:26.625
I want everything.

193
00:12:26.708 --> 00:12:31.416
and you're going to help me
run Bhengu Beauty. the right way.

194
00:12:32.208 --> 00:12:33.458
The way it should be.

195
00:12:47.958 --> 00:12:49.375
- Hello.
<i>- Hi. Bonga.</i>

196
00:12:49.458 --> 00:12:50.458
Who is this?

197
00:12:50.541 --> 00:12:52.221
There's an emergency with Vee.

198
00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:54.291
You're the only one
in her contacts who answered.

199
00:12:54.375 --> 00:12:55.500
What happened?

200
00:12:55.583 --> 00:12:57.142
<i>She's at 31 George Street.</i>

201
00:12:57.166 --> 00:12:58.166
<i>Hurry!</i>

202
00:13:08.500 --> 00:13:10.500
Ah Mr. Bhengu. welcome back.

203
00:13:10.583 --> 00:13:11.875
Your table.

204
00:13:11.958 --> 00:13:12.958
The usual.

205
00:13:13.875 --> 00:13:15.833
- Hey.
- Hey. Mr. Don. how're you doing?

206
00:13:15.916 --> 00:13:18.541
I see you took my advice
about grooming your beard.

207
00:13:18.625 --> 00:13:20.125
I learned from the best.

208
00:13:37.208 --> 00:13:38.250
Thank you.

209
00:13:59.666 --> 00:14:00.666
What?

210
00:14:01.541 --> 00:14:03.875
You seem a little tense.
Are you okay?

211
00:14:05.125 --> 00:14:07.375
This is not really my style.

212
00:14:08.958 --> 00:14:11.166
You're about to be Mrs. Bhengu.

213
00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:13.833
So I asked the stylist
to dress you the part.

214
00:14:17.791 --> 00:14:18.791
Ngcolosi.

215
00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:21.083
I like the sound of that.

216
00:14:25.458 --> 00:14:27.416
Are you ready to order?

217
00:14:28.208 --> 00:14:29.875
Can we have five minutes. please?

218
00:14:34.166 --> 00:14:37.291
It's been a rough couple of months.

219
00:14:37.375 --> 00:14:42.000
Feels like this dark cloud
is just hanging over everything.

220
00:14:42.083 --> 00:14:43.416
That's all over now.

221
00:14:44.458 --> 00:14:48.666
I feel the darkness
of what Mam' Grace did to Thando.

222
00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:51.500
And I still have nightmares
of when she tried to kill me.

223
00:14:53.208 --> 00:14:58.291
I'd feel safer if we had
a spiritual cleansing before our wedding.

224
00:14:58.375 --> 00:14:59.375
Cleansing?

225
00:14:59.833 --> 00:15:01.291
Yeah. a fresh start.

226
00:15:02.166 --> 00:15:03.583
We don't need that.

227
00:15:05.291 --> 00:15:06.541
Ngcolosi...

228
00:15:07.166 --> 00:15:12.375
a cleansing before a new beginning
will make me feel protected.

229
00:15:14.500 --> 00:15:15.916
Please.

230
00:15:18.750 --> 00:15:20.791
Okay. we'll do it.

231
00:15:23.041 --> 00:15:24.208
Waiter?

232
00:15:48.166 --> 00:15:50.958
Anyone here?

233
00:16:13.375 --> 00:16:14.291
Hello?

234
00:16:14.375 --> 00:16:15.625
Are you close?

235
00:16:16.166 --> 00:16:17.708
Put Vee on the line.

236
00:16:17.791 --> 00:16:19.375
I can't. she OD'd.

237
00:16:19.875 --> 00:16:21.166
OD'd?

238
00:16:21.250 --> 00:16:24.958
<i>Yes. she's regaining consciousness.
but we can't leave her alone.</i>

239
00:16:25.041 --> 00:16:26.666
Vee doesn't do drugs.

240
00:16:31.250 --> 00:16:32.500
What?

241
00:16:42.708 --> 00:16:43.875
Greetings.

242
00:16:43.958 --> 00:16:45.541
Your greeting is well received.

243
00:16:46.458 --> 00:16:47.958
You may come in.

244
00:17:01.916 --> 00:17:03.500
The ancestors are here.

245
00:17:03.583 --> 00:17:06.250
They want to speak now.

246
00:17:07.583 --> 00:17:10.875
But they refuse to talk with her here.

247
00:17:12.083 --> 00:17:13.083
Leave. Zinhle.

248
00:17:17.083 --> 00:17:18.208
Of course.

249
00:17:34.625 --> 00:17:37.083
Your ancestors
are showing me your path.

250
00:17:37.625 --> 00:17:40.125
They're showing me your future.

251
00:17:40.750 --> 00:17:45.083
Your journey has led you to a crossroads.

252
00:17:46.291 --> 00:17:53.250
One path leads
to even more power and wealth.

253
00:17:53.333 --> 00:17:55.958
But the other...

254
00:17:56.666 --> 00:17:58.000
Where does it lead to?

255
00:18:00.083 --> 00:18:06.125
I see lotions. children and an old house.

256
00:18:07.291 --> 00:18:10.208
Do these things mean anything to you?

257
00:18:11.458 --> 00:18:12.541
No. nothing.

258
00:18:22.416 --> 00:18:25.416
Your ancestors say you're lying.

259
00:18:26.333 --> 00:18:30.500
They want you to come clean.

260
00:18:30.583 --> 00:18:32.833
I don't know what you're talking about.

261
00:18:34.250 --> 00:18:38.958
There are children crying
and a great fire.

262
00:18:41.041 --> 00:18:43.458
- Let's get out of here.
- Why? What happened?

263
00:18:43.541 --> 00:18:44.916
In the car. Zinhle!

264
00:18:47.791 --> 00:18:48.958
Makhosi.

265
00:18:49.958 --> 00:18:53.125
I know that you have
been through a lot in your life.

266
00:18:53.708 --> 00:18:57.750
But don't you ever make me lie
about the ancestors again.

267
00:18:57.833 --> 00:18:58.916
Here.

268
00:19:12.291 --> 00:19:14.625
- That woman's a quack.
- What did she say?

269
00:19:14.708 --> 00:19:15.875
Hello. Simphiwe.

270
00:19:16.333 --> 00:19:17.958
Can you come to the house?

271
00:19:18.500 --> 00:19:20.250
Yes. straight away. please.

272
00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:22.541
Thank you.

273
00:19:23.041 --> 00:19:24.500
Peter. drive.

274
00:19:29.083 --> 00:19:30.125
What's up?

275
00:19:32.208 --> 00:19:35.541
We lost our only contact.

276
00:19:36.458 --> 00:19:37.541
Still have his number?

277
00:19:37.625 --> 00:19:39.065
He's not going to answer.

278
00:19:39.125 --> 00:19:41.916
It's not about whether he is going
to answer or not. I was thinking...

279
00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:44.309
...maybe you can
find someone to get his address

280
00:19:44.333 --> 00:19:46.166
that's linked to his phone number.

281
00:19:46.250 --> 00:19:48.041
Surely he must have provided it.

282
00:19:48.125 --> 00:19:49.708
Why didn't I think of that?

283
00:19:51.208 --> 00:19:52.500
- Thanks. babe.
- Ah-ah-ah.

284
00:19:55.541 --> 00:19:56.458
You're amazing.

285
00:19:56.541 --> 00:19:57.625
I know.

286
00:20:20.625 --> 00:20:24.083
<i>♪ Not a nigga you can play with
Keep a stone on me like David ♪</i>

287
00:20:24.166 --> 00:20:27.583
<i>♪ I can tell you how my day went
I woke up and got to the cake. yes ♪</i>

288
00:20:27.666 --> 00:20:31.041
<i>♪ Money talk. favorite conversation
Do a lot. I don't really say shit ♪</i>

289
00:20:31.125 --> 00:20:34.500
<i>♪ I swear I ain't hopped out a spaceship
Niggas bite tryna do the same shit ♪</i>

290
00:20:34.583 --> 00:20:36.916
<i>♪ I don't mind
I know niggas try to get to the top ♪</i>

291
00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.583
<i>♪ Just to get they name out there ♪</i>

292
00:20:38.666 --> 00:20:42.333
<i>♪ I just make some sacrifices that
I know they won't make. so it's not fair ♪</i>

293
00:21:35.666 --> 00:21:37.333
Ah!

294
00:21:40.541 --> 00:21:42.166
Hey! Ai!

295
00:21:43.375 --> 00:21:44.375
Oh...

296
00:21:51.875 --> 00:21:56.916
There is a spirit of vengeance.

297
00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:58.833
It's coming after you.

298
00:21:59.833 --> 00:22:02.375
I don't know
if it's in the physical world.

299
00:22:02.458 --> 00:22:04.833
or the spiritual world.

300
00:22:04.916 --> 00:22:08.750
It's protected by pure souls.

301
00:22:09.416 --> 00:22:10.916
Can you help me?

302
00:22:12.250 --> 00:22:14.750
Like I said.
it is protected by pure souls.

303
00:22:14.833 --> 00:22:18.083
I don't know if I'll be able to help you.

304
00:22:18.166 --> 00:22:20.000
You'll be well compensated...

305
00:22:22.083 --> 00:22:23.458
as usual.

306
00:22:28.708 --> 00:22:30.291
I'll be able to help you

307
00:22:31.916 --> 00:22:33.291
only if it reveals itself.

308
00:22:36.166 --> 00:22:37.250
Do it.

309
00:22:43.250 --> 00:22:44.541
Yeah!

310
00:22:44.625 --> 00:22:47.083
The driver's waiting for you downstairs.

311
00:22:47.166 --> 00:22:49.666
It's always
good to see you. my friend.

312
00:22:49.750 --> 00:22:52.208
Yeah. it's always great
to do business with you.

313
00:22:52.291 --> 00:22:53.833
If you need me...

314
00:22:53.916 --> 00:22:55.666
...you know where to find me.

315
00:23:03.500 --> 00:23:04.916
How did it go?

316
00:23:05.000 --> 00:23:06.083
Perfectly.

317
00:23:12.875 --> 00:23:17.416
See. there's no need to worry
about dark spirits anymore now.

318
00:23:19.958 --> 00:23:21.125
What are these?

319
00:23:22.208 --> 00:23:24.375
Something to cleanse and protect us.

320
00:23:25.666 --> 00:23:28.500
We're going to take this
together going forward.

321
00:23:32.583 --> 00:23:33.583
Ah...

322
00:23:39.375 --> 00:23:41.666
The wedding announcement
is going out tomorrow.

323
00:23:43.958 --> 00:23:45.500
Prepare for well wishes.

324
00:23:47.291 --> 00:23:48.458
I can't wait.

325
00:23:59.666 --> 00:24:02.291
Grab a few of these for yourself.

326
00:24:21.916 --> 00:24:23.958
Great. see you soon.

327
00:24:26.416 --> 00:24:27.708
Oh. Son. there you are.

328
00:24:27.791 --> 00:24:30.166
I need you to bring
all the board members here tomorrow.

329
00:24:30.250 --> 00:24:32.684
Make sure they don't know
they've all been invited.

330
00:24:32.708 --> 00:24:34.748
I can do that now.
Where are you going?

331
00:24:34.791 --> 00:24:35.951
Doctor's appointment.

332
00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:38.250
- After hours?
- Exactly!

333
00:24:40.833 --> 00:24:41.833
Okay.

334
00:24:45.541 --> 00:24:47.291
You know. this man

335
00:24:47.375 --> 00:24:51.375
thinks the wedding
will fix his reputation.

336
00:24:51.458 --> 00:24:54.250
The reputation that you have ruined?

337
00:24:55.083 --> 00:24:56.083
<i>Yes.</i>

338
00:24:56.458 --> 00:24:57.875
<i>What am I going to do now?</i>

339
00:24:57.958 --> 00:25:00.000
I'm going to tell you what I did.

340
00:25:00.083 --> 00:25:03.500
I went to the police and told
them that Don murdered Kolobe.

341
00:25:04.125 --> 00:25:05.208
Bonga.

342
00:25:05.291 --> 00:25:08.583
I specifically told you that we cannot
be talking to the police.

343
00:25:08.666 --> 00:25:10.125
What are we supposed to do?

344
00:25:10.208 --> 00:25:13.833
What are we going to do because
I'm getting mysterious calls about Vee?

345
00:25:14.333 --> 00:25:16.166
No. We need help.

346
00:25:16.250 --> 00:25:17.850
This could ruin everything.

347
00:25:19.458 --> 00:25:23.125
Look. Detective Selekane
is a trustworthy man.

348
00:25:23.208 --> 00:25:24.375
<i>How can you be so sure?</i>

349
00:25:24.458 --> 00:25:26.458
My boss referred me to him.
They are friends.

350
00:25:26.541 --> 00:25:28.333
And he told me that

351
00:25:28.416 --> 00:25:32.416
the detective will investigate
and make an arrest.

352
00:25:32.500 --> 00:25:34.875
<i>He will arrest Don
and have him locked up in prison.</i>

353
00:25:34.958 --> 00:25:36.500
I don't know about this.

354
00:25:36.583 --> 00:25:40.875
For once in our lives.
let me take care of us. Please.

355
00:25:40.958 --> 00:25:42.083
Fine.

356
00:25:42.750 --> 00:25:45.250
But I can't make any
sudden moves with Don.

357
00:25:45.333 --> 00:25:48.833
He has to think everything
is moving forward as planned.

358
00:25:59.291 --> 00:26:01.708
- Top up?
- Yeah. thanks. babe.

359
00:26:08.791 --> 00:26:10.000
Oh my gosh!

360
00:26:10.083 --> 00:26:11.083
What?

361
00:26:12.250 --> 00:26:13.166
What is it?

362
00:26:13.250 --> 00:26:14.916
Dad's wedding announcement.

363
00:26:15.625 --> 00:26:17.750
They're getting married
the day after tomorrow.

364
00:26:17.833 --> 00:26:19.500
Why are they in such a hurry?

365
00:26:19.583 --> 00:26:22.583
He was going to get married
after the heart attack anyway.

366
00:26:23.666 --> 00:26:26.458
I just
don't know what's in it for Zinhle.

367
00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:30.166
No. I can't let this happen.

368
00:26:31.000 --> 00:26:33.500
We need to find out
who this Bonga person is ASAP.

369
00:26:33.583 --> 00:26:36.833
because I... I just know Zinhle
is behind this somehow.

370
00:26:37.708 --> 00:26:39.541
So. how close are you?

371
00:26:40.708 --> 00:26:44.791
Zandi's friend says she can get us
a current address by tomorrow. So...

372
00:26:45.958 --> 00:26:46.958
Okay.

373
00:27:04.208 --> 00:27:05.458
Uh... Detective.

374
00:27:06.250 --> 00:27:08.458
I got a message
that you wanted to see me.

375
00:27:09.750 --> 00:27:10.958
Hey. man.

376
00:27:12.250 --> 00:27:15.000
I spoke to your boss
at the security company.

377
00:27:16.708 --> 00:27:17.875
About?

378
00:27:17.958 --> 00:27:18.833
Mm.

379
00:27:18.916 --> 00:27:25.583
This whole incident seems
to have caused you a lot of stress.

380
00:27:25.666 --> 00:27:26.708
Hmm.

381
00:27:26.791 --> 00:27:28.166
Don't you want some time off?

382
00:27:28.250 --> 00:27:31.125
I'm not stressed. I don't need time off.

383
00:27:38.583 --> 00:27:39.791
You do.

384
00:27:45.833 --> 00:27:47.041
Hey. man.

385
00:27:47.125 --> 00:27:49.833
Take a few days off. Eh? It comes with...

386
00:27:49.916 --> 00:27:51.083
...full pay!

387
00:27:51.625 --> 00:27:52.625
Huh?

388
00:27:56.291 --> 00:27:58.083
With bonus. of course.

389
00:28:19.208 --> 00:28:21.833
Zinhle. I really messed up.

390
00:28:21.916 --> 00:28:24.208
I need to disappear for a while.

391
00:28:24.291 --> 00:28:26.666
I need to see you before I leave.

392
00:28:29.708 --> 00:28:32.508
All the major
media networks have confirmed already.

393
00:28:32.541 --> 00:28:34.221
That's fantastic.

394
00:28:34.291 --> 00:28:35.291
Oh. sorry.

395
00:28:36.666 --> 00:28:38.541
- I've got to take this.
- Sure.

396
00:28:41.666 --> 00:28:43.750
Aw. pre-wedding jitters?

397
00:28:44.708 --> 00:28:46.083
Yeah. Yeah.

398
00:28:46.166 --> 00:28:49.041
Don't worry about it.
Everything's going to be perfect.

399
00:28:49.125 --> 00:28:50.833
- Uh...
- Yeah.

400
00:28:50.916 --> 00:28:52.166
Duty calls.

401
00:28:52.875 --> 00:28:54.083
I'll see you later.

402
00:28:55.625 --> 00:28:57.583
- What baby wants...
- Baby gets!

403
00:28:59.791 --> 00:29:01.375
I actually need a charger.

404
00:29:01.458 --> 00:29:02.875
Of course. you can use mine.

405
00:29:02.958 --> 00:29:05.875
Now. let's get you ready in that dress.

406
00:29:05.958 --> 00:29:08.625
- Okay.
- You must be so excited!

407
00:29:12.375 --> 00:29:13.375
Ma?

408
00:29:13.916 --> 00:29:15.375
Yes. son. is it done?

409
00:29:16.083 --> 00:29:17.083
Yep.

410
00:29:17.833 --> 00:29:18.875
Wonderful.

411
00:29:18.958 --> 00:29:19.875
Sit down.

412
00:29:19.958 --> 00:29:23.291
Let me tell you
exactly how this is going to play out.

413
00:29:26.250 --> 00:29:27.833
Is it a current address?

414
00:29:30.166 --> 00:29:31.291
Perfect. thanks.

415
00:29:32.416 --> 00:29:34.000
Babe. I got an address.

416
00:29:34.583 --> 00:29:36.291
- Really? Where is it?
- Yes.

417
00:29:36.375 --> 00:29:37.291
It's in Soweto.

418
00:29:37.375 --> 00:29:38.750
We also got a surname.

419
00:29:38.833 --> 00:29:41.666
- It's Selepe.
- Oh. that's... that's great.

420
00:29:41.750 --> 00:29:42.958
Thank you.

421
00:29:49.500 --> 00:29:52.083
You're coming with me. right?

422
00:29:54.291 --> 00:29:55.291
Yeah.

423
00:29:56.666 --> 00:29:57.666
Okay.

424
00:30:59.625 --> 00:31:01.105
How do you know Kolobe?

425
00:31:14.791 --> 00:31:16.833
I don't know
what you're talking about.

426
00:31:19.416 --> 00:31:21.875
Then why are you
bothering Detective Selekane...

427
00:31:21.958 --> 00:31:23.250
...about his death

428
00:31:26.750 --> 00:31:28.250
