429
00:31:31.250 --> 00:31:32.666
I don't want your money.

430
00:31:33.750 --> 00:31:38.666
I want to see you and Grace
in prison for what you did.

431
00:31:38.750 --> 00:31:40.583
And what exactly did we do?

432
00:31:40.666 --> 00:31:42.458
This thing Grace and I did.

433
00:31:45.541 --> 00:31:47.041
You don't remember?

434
00:31:50.958 --> 00:31:55.708
I'm one of the children
you tested bleaches on.

435
00:31:57.166 --> 00:31:59.625
And then you burned us alive.

436
00:31:59.708 --> 00:32:00.708
Remember that?

437
00:32:00.791 --> 00:32:02.351
And you survived the fire?

438
00:32:02.416 --> 00:32:03.333
Yes.

439
00:32:03.416 --> 00:32:04.833
It's over Don.

440
00:32:09.916 --> 00:32:11.250
Please don't shoot.

441
00:32:11.333 --> 00:32:12.625
I'm so sorry.

442
00:32:13.208 --> 00:32:14.833
No? You...

443
00:32:15.333 --> 00:32:16.875
You don't remember?

444
00:32:17.666 --> 00:32:18.666
No.

445
00:32:18.708 --> 00:32:21.166
I was just a young boy.

446
00:32:22.708 --> 00:32:25.125
I tried to run away.

447
00:32:25.625 --> 00:32:27.708
You caught me
and burned me like some animal.

448
00:32:27.791 --> 00:32:29.083
You don't remember that?

449
00:32:30.166 --> 00:32:31.291
I'm sorry.

450
00:32:37.166 --> 00:32:38.458
Hey!

451
00:32:38.541 --> 00:32:40.375
Don't come closer!

452
00:32:42.708 --> 00:32:45.500
You don't remember anything at all?

453
00:32:46.916 --> 00:32:48.356
See. everything I do...

454
00:32:49.666 --> 00:32:52.166
the women. the houses.
the trips. the cars...

455
00:32:52.250 --> 00:32:54.333
...it's all to make me forget.

456
00:32:54.416 --> 00:32:55.833
You want me

457
00:32:56.541 --> 00:32:57.666
to feel sorry for you?

458
00:32:57.750 --> 00:33:00.184
- I don't want you to pity me.
- What do you want?

459
00:33:00.208 --> 00:33:02.125
- Just go ahead and shoot me. Shoot me!
- Hey!

460
00:33:05.833 --> 00:33:07.208
I deserve to die.

461
00:33:08.583 --> 00:33:10.500
God knows. I look forward to it.

462
00:33:11.708 --> 00:33:14.875
You... you don't deserve to be a killer.

463
00:33:17.083 --> 00:33:18.166
I destroyed your life.

464
00:33:18.250 --> 00:33:20.708
Don. Don. Don... Don!

465
00:33:20.791 --> 00:33:22.333
I don't want to do it again.

466
00:33:23.541 --> 00:33:24.750
Just lower the gun.

467
00:33:27.791 --> 00:33:28.958
I will repent.

468
00:33:29.458 --> 00:33:31.916
I will do what you think is right.

469
00:33:32.833 --> 00:33:34.666
Just lower the gun. son.

470
00:33:35.625 --> 00:33:37.166
I will take my punishment.

471
00:33:43.958 --> 00:33:47.958
Mm!
And it is dripping from head to toe.

472
00:33:48.041 --> 00:33:49.666
Fits like a glove. right?

473
00:33:49.750 --> 00:33:52.083
It does. Actually. let me take a video.

474
00:33:53.583 --> 00:33:57.708
Mmm... Get a little bit of you
fluffing your dress.

475
00:33:57.833 --> 00:34:00.916
Yes. girl. You looking so fly!

476
00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:03.333
May I please...
may I please have my phone.

477
00:34:03.416 --> 00:34:04.416
Oh. yes.

478
00:34:09.750 --> 00:34:11.166
There you go.

479
00:34:11.250 --> 00:34:12.250
Thank you.

480
00:34:13.166 --> 00:34:15.458
Let's fluff up here in the back.

481
00:34:20.541 --> 00:34:22.791
<i>Zinhle. I really messed up.</i>

482
00:34:22.875 --> 00:34:27.083
<i>I need to disappear for a while.
Please come see me before I leave.</i>

483
00:34:29.166 --> 00:34:31.447
Can somebody please
get me out of this dress?

484
00:34:32.250 --> 00:34:35.125
Somebody. please.
get me out of this dress right now.

485
00:34:41.958 --> 00:34:43.125
Oh. shit.

486
00:34:46.000 --> 00:34:48.080
I think that's
the house there on the right.

487
00:34:48.125 --> 00:34:49.125
- Yes?
- Yeah.

488
00:34:53.666 --> 00:34:55.351
- What is Dad doing here?
- What?

489
00:34:55.375 --> 00:34:56.833
Thando. what is Dad doing here?

490
00:34:56.916 --> 00:34:58.750
I think that's your daughter.

491
00:34:59.291 --> 00:35:00.208
Ah. fuck.

492
00:35:00.291 --> 00:35:01.666
What is he doing here?

493
00:35:02.333 --> 00:35:03.208
Dad!

494
00:35:03.291 --> 00:35:04.875
What are you doing here?

495
00:35:04.958 --> 00:35:07.333
- You can't be here! Just go!
- Dad. just please. Listen

496
00:35:07.416 --> 00:35:08.750
Dad!

497
00:35:30.125 --> 00:35:32.250
Bonga. answer your phone.

498
00:35:38.791 --> 00:35:40.458
Ladies and gentlemen.

499
00:35:41.583 --> 00:35:43.791
I know you're all confused
why you're here.

500
00:35:45.708 --> 00:35:47.166
It will be very clear.

501
00:35:48.583 --> 00:35:52.708
In front of you are
confidential medical records. open them.

502
00:35:59.791 --> 00:36:01.916
I've been hiding
my husband's secret for a year.

503
00:36:02.791 --> 00:36:05.708
but he's getting worse.
and there's nothing I can do to help him.

504
00:36:06.750 --> 00:36:10.208
He's fired two CEOs
in less than two months.

505
00:36:11.041 --> 00:36:14.416
And suddenly he's marrying
a much younger employee days after...

506
00:36:19.458 --> 00:36:22.916
Don Bhengu is mentally unfit to lead.

507
00:36:23.958 --> 00:36:25.291
We need to take action now

508
00:36:25.375 --> 00:36:27.708
before he runs
the company into the ground.

509
00:36:30.416 --> 00:36:32.333
It's time to pick a new head

510
00:36:33.708 --> 00:36:35.250
of Bhengu Beauty.

511
00:36:47.958 --> 00:36:51.166
<i>♪ Hanging around waiting to die ♪</i>

512
00:36:54.083 --> 00:36:58.958
<i>♪ Never been quite satisfied ♪</i>

513
00:36:59.958 --> 00:37:02.208
<i>♪ A siren song... ♪</i>

514
00:37:03.000 --> 00:37:04.041
Bonga?

515
00:37:05.833 --> 00:37:06.833
Bonga?

516
00:37:10.208 --> 00:37:11.458
Bonga?

517
00:37:15.000 --> 00:37:16.166
Bonga?

518
00:37:22.666 --> 00:37:25.708
Bonga! No. no. no! Bonga!

519
00:37:27.041 --> 00:37:28.583
No. No.

520
00:37:28.666 --> 00:37:30.458
Oh my God!

521
00:37:30.541 --> 00:37:31.791
What happened?

522
00:37:35.333 --> 00:37:37.250
I'm so sorry. I'm sorry.

523
00:37:37.333 --> 00:37:39.583
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry...

